                        },
                        {
                            "tip_text": "Dress comfortably and bring a light layer, as air conditioning in the observation lounges can make it chilly compared to the outside."
                        },
                        {
                            "tip_text": "The Dubai Mall's taxi and parking areas can be busy even in the early morning; plan your transportation in advance, and follow clear signs for Burj Khalifa entry."
                        },
                        {
                            "tip_text": "After the sunrise and observation experience, you can enjoy refreshments included with your Platinum ticket in the Sky Lounge. Consider a post-visit stroll through The Dubai Mall or watching the fountains if you're staying after your tour."
